text: The following lists events that happened in 1966 in Iceland. ==Incumbents== *President - Ásgeir Ásgeirsson *Prime Minister - Bjarni Benediktsson ==Events== ==Births== Baltasar Kormákur *27 February - Baltasar Kormákur, actor, theater and film director, and film producer *10 March - Margrét Vilhjálmsdóttir, actress *23 May - Árni Páll Árnason, politician. *31 August - Eagle Egilsson, cinematographer and television director *27 September - Sigurður Jónsson, footballer *12 October - Hanna Birna Kristjánsdóttir, politician. *3 December - Ólöf Nordal, politician ==Deaths== ==References== Category:1960s in Iceland Iceland Iceland Category:Years of the 20th century in Iceland
title: 1966 in Iceland
